Class StudentUI

java.lang.Object
boundaries.ChoiceUI
boundaries.StudentUI
All Implemented Interfaces:
GeneralUI, HiddenInputUI
public class StudentUI
extends ChoiceUI
implements HiddenInputUI
UI for student users. Meant to abstract student system from users
